    <item>
      <title>中国采取措施阻止苹果和比亚迪将生产转移到亚洲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/china-moves-to-stall-apple-byd-production-shifts-across-asia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，中国正加大对印度和东南亚高科技制造业所需的员工和专用设备的出境限制，此举可能是为了防止企业在美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普上台后因关税上调而转移生产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/china-moves-to-stall-apple-byd-production-shifts-across-asia</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 10:12:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>三星电子大改革：高管奖金将以股票形式发放</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/samsung-executives-to-get-part-of-bonus-in-stock-in-big-revamp</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三星电子公司首次决定以股票而非现金形式支付高管部分奖金，将高管薪酬与股票表现挂钩，而目前该公司正陷入芯片制造困境。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/samsung-executives-to-get-part-of-bonus-in-stock-in-big-revamp</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:58:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>肯尼亚将在反鲁托运动中加强社交媒体管控</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/kenya-to-tighten-control-of-social-media-amid-anti-ruto-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[肯尼亚计划加强对社交媒体的监管，以应对最近针对总统威廉·鲁托 (William Ruto) 的恶意网络攻击，因为对其压制异议行为的批评日益增多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/kenya-to-tighten-control-of-social-media-amid-anti-ruto-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:39:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>私募股权公司利用南非莱利银行寻找肯尼亚糖果制造商股权的买家</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pe-firms-tap-nedbank-to-find-buyer-for-kenya-candy-maker-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，两家私募股权公司已聘请南非莱利银行集团有限公司 (Nedbank Group Ltd.) 出售其在东非最大糖果制造商的股份，价值超过 1 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pe-firms-tap-nedbank-to-find-buyer-for-kenya-candy-maker-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 08:14:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
